        { dimension:'EU/EMA — All Indications', status:'UNMET REGULATORY NEED', detail:'No EMA authorisation. 3+ years post-FDA approval for aesthetics indication. Largest regulatory gap in the asset lifecycle. Freyr EU affiliate network (850+) and freya.intelligence are the solution. No incumbent identified.' },
