      landExpandTransform:"LAND (Current): Country expansion regulatory services in Americas. Protect, deepen, and activate EU/EMA and China NMPA regulatory programmes immediately. freya.intelligence POC in H2 2026 establishes technology entry point. | EXPAND (12-18 Months): PV programme management, MLR Review, Medical Affairs — all three tied to DAXXIFY's active commercial programmes. Enter all three service lines before Crown procurement review locks vendor roster. Target: 60-70% revenue growth from Growth Services additions. freya.intelligence SaaS converted. | TRANSFORM (24-36 Months): VIA for China NMPA and multi-indication variation management. freya fusion as DAXXIFY's global RIM platform as EU approval generates multi-market lifecycle complexity. Freyr is Crown's preferred regulatory partner across Revance and potentially across other Crown portfolio companies.",
